msgid "group_by_arrival_time_method()"
msgstr "group_by_arrival_time_method()"

#: ../../source/multiplayer/waitpages.rst:130
msgid ""
"Before November 2019, this was a method called ``get_players_for_group``,"
" and it was on the Page, not the Subsession. We recommend switching to "
"the new format."
